---
permalink: /success.html
layout: base.njk
documentTitle: "WhatCable Pro - Purchase Complete"
description: "Activate your WhatCable Pro licence key."
robots: noindex
twitterCard: summary
extraHead: |
  <style>
    .success-main {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 48px 20px;
    }
    .success-card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      padding: 48px;
      max-width: 540px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .success-card .check {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #e6f4ee;
      color: var(--good);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .success-card .check svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; }
    .success-card h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 12px; color: var(--ink); }
    .success-card .subtitle { color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 32px; font-size: 15px; }
    .steps {
      text-align: left;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .steps h2 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .step-num {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }
    .step-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.5; }
    .step-text strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
    .back { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; }
    .back a { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
    .back a:hover { color: var(--accent-strong); }
  </style>
---
<main class="success-main">
  <div class="success-card">
    <div class="check" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h1>You're all set</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Your WhatCable Pro licence key is on its way to your inbox. Check your email and follow these steps to activate.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <h2>How to activate</h2>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Check your email</strong> for a message from noreply@whatcable.uk with your licence key.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Right-click WhatCable</strong> in the menu bar and click <strong>Licence</strong>.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Paste your key</strong> into the licence field and activate.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Pro features unlock</strong> immediately. Works on up to 2 Macs.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="back">No email after a few minutes? Check your spam folder or <a href="/support">contact support</a>.</p>
  </div>
</main>
